      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="homepage-service">
      <h3 class="homepage-service__title">
        Your next phase
      </h3>
      <p class="homepage-service__paragraph">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Officia officiis, inventore iusto consequuntur.
