        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Officia officiis, inventore iusto consequuntur.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="homepage-latest">
    <h2 class="homepage-latest__title">
      Who we have partnered with
    </h2>

    <% current_page.data.projects.each do |project| %>
      <a class="homepage-tile" href="#">
        <div class="homepage-tile__content">
          <img class="homepage-tile__image" src="<%= project.image %>" alt="<%= project.name %>">

          <h3 class="homepage-tile__title">
            <%= project.name %>
          </h3>

          <p class="homepage-tile__paragraph">
            <%= project.description %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="component">
    <div class="component__tile">
      <div class="text-tile">
        <h2 class="text-tile__title">
          What about you?
        </h2>

        <p class="text-tile__paragraph">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Quaerat nulla itaque ex voluptatibus magni sunt alias, sequi, molestias aspernatur, enim asperiores numquam placeat dignissimos ipsa quam recusandae consectetur illum maxime!
